<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也拜托<delay20 /><colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
建造了自己的房子啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是恭喜呀！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望这是<tag a="110" b="4" />你<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在<tag a="110" b="33" />的<delay8 />
美好未来的一个开端！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />我看到了哦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的家<delay20 />变得这么大了呀！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了能扩建成这样，<delay20 />
你一定付出了相当多的汗水吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这正是你努力的成果呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
变得更为气派的<colour id="1" />Nook商店<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经去过了吗？
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那里陈列的商品也更加充实，<delay20 />
真是越来越便利了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />豆狸<colour id="65535" />和<colour id="3" />粒狸<colour id="65535" />他们<delay20 />
真是经营有方，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />未来可期呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家都期待着的<delay8 />
<colour id="1" /><tag a="110" b="8" />博物馆<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />
终于落成了！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没想到居然能建得如此宏伟，<delay20 />
说老实话，我都被吓到了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />傅达<colour id="65535" /><delay20 />挺能干的嘛<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />终于，<delay8 />这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上也造好了<colour id="1" />裁缝屋<colour id="65535" />呀！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不愧是经营服装生意的店铺，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />装修的品位也很紧跟潮流呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然<delay20 />网购也很便利，<delay20 />
但有很多东西不拿在手里是不知道的。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />岛上能开一家店<delay8 />真让人高兴呀。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多亏造好了新的路，<delay8 />
现在可以轻松到悬崖上去了，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可真是<delay8 />帮了我大忙呀。
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />从高处俯瞰广阔的大海，<delay20 />
会有一种心灵被洗涤的感觉，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常有治愈效果呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">最近岛上搬来的<delay8 />
新居民<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是和你关系非常亲密呀？
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />不知为何就有这种感觉呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了能让对方<delay8 />喜欢上这座<tag a="110" b="32" />，<delay20 />
大家一起努力吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />博物馆<colour id="65535" />的艺术品展览开展以来，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />你去过吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以有机会亲眼<delay8 />欣赏到那么多佳作，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是件让人很开心的事，
你不这样认为吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>